70" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Donald-Trump-and-Taylor-Swift.-Credit-Michael-Ciaglo-and-Gareth-Cattermole-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="唐纳德·特朗普和泰勒·斯威夫特。图片来源：Michael Ciaglo 和 Gareth Cattermole，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Donald-Trump-and-Taylor-Swift.-Credit-Michael-Ciaglo-and-Gareth-Cattermole-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Donald-Trump-and-Taylor-Swift.-Credit-Michael-Ciaglo-and-Gareth-Cattermole-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Donald-Trump-and-Taylor-Swift.-Credit-Michael-Ciaglo-and-Gareth-Cattermole-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Donald-Trump-and-Taylor-Swift.-Credit-Michael-Ciaglo-and-Gareth-Cattermole-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Donald-Trump-and-Taylor-Swift.-Credit-Michael-Ciaglo-and-Gareth-Cattermole-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Donald-Trump-and-Taylor-Swift.-Credit-Michael-Ciaglo-and-Gareth-Cattermole-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">唐纳德·特朗普</a>公开了<a href="/artists/Taylor-Swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>支持副总统卡玛拉·哈里斯的事，并表示这位歌手“可能会付出代价”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/taylor-swift-live-in-edinburgh-3763814">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 爱丁堡现场演唱会：“Eras Tour”终于登陆英国</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨晚（9 月 10 日）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-the-first-trump-vs-harris-presidential-debate-it-was-like-watching-muhammad-ali-3792635">特朗普和哈里斯在费城展开了他们的第一场，也可能是唯一一场辩论</a>。双方在民意调查中几乎势均力敌，选民定于 11 月 5 日投票。</p><p>在辩论中，特朗普主要重申了他集会上的言论，而哈里斯则利用她的平台分享了她对国家的计划，并回应了她在竞选期间收到的批评。当晚最受关注的时刻之一是，这位前总统试图推动有关俄亥俄州斯普林菲尔德海地移民的指控，这些指控现已被揭穿，这些移民被指控绑架当地宠物并吃掉它们。</p><p>辩论结束后，斯威夫特在她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-endorsement-of-kamala-harris-for-president-3792514">Instagram官方账户上表达了她对哈里斯的支持</a>。这些评论是在选举前两个月发表的。</p><p> “我将在 2024 年总统选举中投票给卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 和蒂姆·沃尔兹 (Tim Walz)。我投票给@kamalaharris，因为她为权利而战，我认为需要一名战士来捍卫它们，”她的帖子标题写道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_wtAOKOW1z/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886